.TH PRE\-COMMIT\-HELP "1" "February 2025" "" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
.B pre\-commit\-help
\[en]
Show help for a specific command
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B pre\-commit\ help
.RB [ \-h ]
.RI [ help_cmd ]
.SH OPTIONS
.SS "POSITIONAL\ ARGUMENTS"
.TP
.I help_cmd
Command to show help for.
.SS "OPTIONAL\ ARGUMENTS"
.TP
.B \-h\fR,\ \fB\-\-help
Show a help message and exit.
.SH "SEE\ ALSO"
